milestones.description: West Indies's 108-run win against England is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 92-run win against England
Viv Richards has become the top scorer in ODIs with 971 runs, going past Greg Chappell's 953
John Lever and Bairstow's 30-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Geoff Arnold and Peter Lever
Alvin Kallicharran and Viv Richards's 109-run partnership is WI's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Clive Lloyd and Greenidge
